===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|sort||}}

#{{transitive}} To [[separate]] according to certain [[criterion|criteria]].
#{{transitive}} To [[arrange]] into in some order, especially [[numerically]], [[alphabetically]] or [[chronologically]].

====Synonyms====
*(''separate according to certain criteria''): [[categorise]]/[[categorize]], [[class]], [[classify]], [[group]]
*(''arrange into some sort of order''): [[order]], [[rank]]

